            h5 <u>The second fight</u>  Kara vs Tais 
            p.
              Tais defeated Kara in the first round. Her aggressive attack, consisting mainly of strikes with kicks, the majority of which missed the target by some way, resulted in bringing the fight into the ground, where Tais managed to get the top position.<br>
              Continuing to wrestle on top Tais tried to armlock Kara. The young girl wrenched herself free but while doing so, she got her neck caught in the grip of Tais, who won by a choke as a result.
